androidx.test.internal.runner.intent

Class IntentMonitorImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.test.internal.runner.intent.IntentMonitorImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IntentMonitor

    public final class IntentMonitorImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements IntentMonitor
    Monitors all outgoing Intents and signals intent to all registered Callbacks.

    This intent monitor will be notified by MonitoringInstrumentation when a new activity was started using Activity#startActivity(Intent).

Generated javadoc for the new package structure to make it clearer which packages are bundled with the Android operating system, and which are packaged with your app's APK. Going forward, the android.* package hierarchy will be reserved for Android packages that ship with the operating system; other packages will be issued in the new androidx.* package hiearchy.
